HEADWORD: Paludism
<hw>Pa*lu"dism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>The morbid phenomena produced by dwelling among marshes; malarial
disease or disposition.</def>⟦br⟧
